### Parameters


`Request` - object

A JSON request object

### Request

``` java
curl --location --request POST 'https://dash.getblock.io/mainnet/' 
--header 'x-api-key: YOUR-API-KEY' 
--header 'Content-Type: application/json' 
--data-raw '{"jsonrpc": "2.0",
"method": "getblocktemplate",
"params": [null],
"id": "getblock.io"}'
```
